This paper deals with conversation modeling and natural language processing, which are typically associated with the sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves information retrieval (cs.IR) and social and information networks (cs.SI) as it deals with conversation dynamics and structures in online platforms.
